     Acoustica is a comprehensive audio  editor  for  recording,  editing,
     mixing and mastering. The intuitive user interface was designed  with
     speed, accuracy and ease-of-use in mind and offers  a  large  set  of
     high quality processing tools to make your recordings sound the best.
     The consistent workflow simplifies your  audio  production  work  and
     batch processing, powerful audio restoration tools  as  well  as  Red
     Book compatible CD burning is also included. 
     

       [b]requirements:[/b]

     A Pentium IV or higher
     Minimum 256 MB RAM (1 GB recommended)
     A Windows MME or ASIO compatible sound card
     Windows 10, 8, 7, Vista or XP
